\lang english
6.2 Policy Lifecycle and Change Control
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
Updates to the Policy Manual shall follow this change control workflow.
 The approval tiers defined in Step 3 apply to both new policy creation and revision of existing policies.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\series bold
\lang english
Identification
\series default
:
 The IT Director shall identify needed revisions based on the review triggers in Section 6.1.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\series bold
\lang english
